    "title": "DigiBatt Project Handbook and Risk Management Table",
    "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.13918328",
    "publication_date": "2024-10-11",
    "description": "<p>This deliverable sets out the management guidelines which will be followed in the<br>DigiBatt project. The main purpose of the deliverable is to provide guidance to<br>project participants to enable the efficient implementation of the action. The<br>deliverable contains information and links to relevant documents, files and<br>templates to be used in the project, including, where appropriate, links to the Grant<br>Agreement and Consortium Agreement. Information in the legally binding Grant<br>Agreement and Consortium Agreement takes precedence over information<br>contained in this handbook. All partners are responsible for fulfilling contractual<br>obligations the Grant Agreement and Consortium Agreement.</p>",
